text: Einius Petkus (born 29 May 1970) is a Lithuanian rower. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Lithuanian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Lithuania Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vilnius
